# Terraform
**/.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
.terraform.lock.hcl
crash.log

# Sensitive — only .example files are committed
**/terraform.tfvars
**/distros/*.tfvars
!**/distros/*.tfvars.example
**/kubeconfig-harvester.yaml
*.pem
!shared/private-ca.pem
*.key

# Build artifacts
**/reports/

# Claude Code / AI — committed to GitLab, stripped from GitHub by sync-to-github
# (no gitignore needed; sync job uses --invert-paths for these)

# Environment (local dev secrets)
.env

# OS
.DS_Store
